{"title":"农民办工厂  生产大变样","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民办工厂  生产大变样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民办工厂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民办工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"简单又便当；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闲时当工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙时把地上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本钱自己积，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原料不出乡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工具十来样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古庙做厂坊；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了钻技术，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进城跑一趟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习三五天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白把变内行；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗肥能自造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农具会改装；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土产自加工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还能烧硫磺；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢磨碾米面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器缝衣裳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天黑喇叭响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电灯明晃晃；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民办工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产大变样！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（山西晋城，马国良辑）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提前实现机械化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你投资，我献房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家协作建工厂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖铁矿，炼成钢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造成机器都都响；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提前实现机械化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看排场不排场！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河南登封）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小工厂，作用大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能造水车修犁耙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从今不再跑城里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农具缺损全不怕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河北东光）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一家一木一块砖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千家万户堆成山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"废砖闲料盖工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社里生产翻几翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河北东光）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处机轮声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社社办工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处机轮声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推磨不用牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家安电灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农村像城市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"街道宽又明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行人惊相问："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“此处是天津？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河北东光）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前天在会上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈论办工厂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天午饭前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厂牌挂门上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今晚月正南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地里水车响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河北东光）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山窝窝里建工厂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山窝窝里建工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去想也不敢想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨夜开会刚策划，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今早机器运到乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千人万人争着扛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛到祠堂去安装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年大事一朝办，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机声跟着笑声响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（福建福安）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平地一声春雷响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枫堂要建造纸厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每日造纸四万担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子听了速拍掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人听了把话讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山角里头造工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那能这么便当？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用十五年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也得十年长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人话音还未落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽车呜呜开进山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车门一开人群下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一来就是几百个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是工人老大哥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们身强力又壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七手八脚力量多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破庙里头安机器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器轰轰光唱歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声一起响十湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓得老虎连夜逃荒坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响得枫堂人民笑呵呵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山角里办工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金银财宝山区多！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（浙江庆元）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖拉机出了厂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖拉机，新生号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"4月20日出了厂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖拉机，身子小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拐弯抹角真灵巧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖拉机，是件宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕地运输都能搞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖拉机，真正好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带动电滚如飞跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新生厂的干劲高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众努力党领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大胆试制拖拉机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大部零件自己造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只用三十零八天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安装完毕田间跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（辽宁复县）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小型发电站"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮红日照九州，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有穿有吃没有愁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了小型发电站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节省劳力节省油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自动磨儿团团转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜来电灯照四周。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四川重庆倪天保）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化学工厂办起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民兄弟笑颜开；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兜兜禾苗雷钵人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷子沉沉垂下来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（福建泰宁）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}